text: On further review, no need to throw an exception.  The same encryption/decryption method that works with xlsx works with xlsb.  I added a unit test with test file to confirm this.

Broke the build with the new unit test. :( 

The test file requires unlimited jce.  I added an if clause that tests for unlimited JCE; if no unlimited JCE, skip the test.
